{"tid":1827800,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港局勢轉趨穩定，南韓政府下調旅遊警示級別。","createTime":"2020-01-17T08:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T10:57:58.000Z","uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b311778b2d93084ea2ffc463f9399e1a8a5675df","tid":1827800,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:45:26.000Z","msg":"【南韓下調對港旅遊警示】<br />\n<br />\n南韓外交部今日（1月17日）表示，鑑於香港局勢趨穩，將針對香港全境的旅遊預警，由第二級的「謹慎前往」，下調到第一級的「注意安全」。<br />\n<br />\n據《韓聯社》報道，南韓外交部稱，將繼續注視香港示威動向和治安形勢，適時調整預警級別。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-17-2020/59122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-17-2020%2F59122&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcymrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=c0f7c1da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-17-2020/59122</a><br />\n<br />\n#南韓 #香港 #旅遊警示"},{"pid":"b4aeef7683713893d2ec9e0bc2e0b89d2ebf3540","tid":1827800,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/bv8qZFE.gif\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/F9ieS0E.gif\" />"},{"pid":"9551be68f7a538c74e27ca78350fc1581315d9e5","tid":1827800,"uid":66260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:48:50.000Z","msg":"連泡菜都覺得場運動靜左"},{"pid":"a0411a1ee213d9f7d4228967dfe5d85be018d733","tid":1827800,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de728fd080c2a72b68e408232140e2eb1aee5655","tid":1827800,"uid":126305,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9551be68f7a538c74e27ca78350fc1581315d9e5","tid":1827800,"uid":66260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:48:50.000Z","msg":"連泡菜都覺得場運動靜左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:09:18.000Z","msg":"靜佐咪送D韓國人黎香港旅行囉<br />\n好過支那